    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>
        This enumeration is used to control the behavior of 
        <see cref="M:Mono.Rocks.TextReaderRocks.Lines(System.IO.TextReader,Mono.Rocks.TextReaderRocksOptions)" />
        and
        <see cref="M:Mono.Rocks.TextReaderRocks.Words(System.IO.TextReader,Mono.Rocks.TextReaderRocksOptions)" />
